                            <comment id="14144557" author="ashakirin" created="Tue, 23 Sep 2014 08:45:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The result of UrilInfo.getAbsolutePath() is dependent on address set in JAXRSServerFactoryBean:&lt;br/&gt;
sf.setAddress(&quot;http://localhost:8888/&quot;); - works correct&lt;br/&gt;
sf.setAddress(&quot;http://localhost:8888&quot;); - produces &quot;http://localhost:8888bookstore/books/123&quot;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;IMO we should check this and append path separator, if necessary&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14144646" author="sergey_beryozkin" created="Tue, 23 Sep 2014 10:38:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Indeed, UriInfoImpl.getAbsolutePathAsString needs to have an extra check, thanks&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
